name: Valencia Typhoon Ice Laminate Countertop
description: Update the look of your room with the sophisticated and dramatic design of the Hampton Bay 96 in. Valencia Typhoon Ice laminate countertop. This countertop provides a virtually seamless appearance and the built-in backsplash provides no crevices where dirt and grime collect. The full-wrap ogee edge helps provide a unique and pleasant appearance.
